data.description: Welcome to this meticulously maintained 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence conveniently nestled near CR 17, offering easy access to shopping and restaurants. The heart of the home lies in its inviting eat-in kitchen, seamlessly connecting to the living room, creating a delightful flow for both everyday living and entertaining. The well-thought-out split floorplan ensures privacy, with a spacious main suite boasting a large bathroom featuring a double vanity and a coveted walk-in closet, freshly painted and new flooring. The convenience extends to the main floor mudroom/laundry area, making daily tasks a breeze. This home is a perfect blend of comfort and functionality, providing a warm and welcoming environment for its fortunate residents.
